<div class="main-and-aside r">
  
  <div class="main content-container" role="main">
    
      <div class="article-teaser">
        Over Christmas and the New Year, most of the TfL network is open. However, today there are changes to services and planned works that may affect your journey.
        
      </div>
    
    <div class="on-this-page">
      <p>There are changes and planned works on the following services today. All our other services are running normally.</p>

<p>See&nbsp;our <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2018-12-26T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2018-12-26T23%3a59%3a59">Status updates map for&nbsp;Wednesday 26&nbsp;December</a>&nbsp;for Tube, Overground, TfL Rail, DLR and tram services.</p>

<h2>Tube</h2>

<p>A reduced Sunday service is running today:</p>

<ul>
	<li>First trains will run from about 07:45</li>
	<li>Services will be reduced from&nbsp;about 20:00</li>
	<li>Last trains will be at weekday times</li>
	<li>No District line service between Earl's Court and Kensington (Olympia)</li>
	<li>No service on the Waterloo &amp; City line</li>
</ul>

<hr />
<h2>London Overground</h2>

<p>There are no&nbsp;London Overground services today.</p>

<p>Follow <a href="http://twitter.com/LDNOverground">&#64;LDNOverground</a> for news and service information.</p>

<hr />
<h2>TfL Rail</h2>

<p>There are no TfL Rail services today.</p>

<p>Follow <a href="http://twitter.com/TfLRail">&#64;TfLRail</a> for news and service information.</p>

<hr />
<h2>DLR</h2>

<p>A reduced service is running.</p>

<ul>
	<li>Trains are running every 10 minutes on all routes</li>
	<li>There is no service between Bow Church and Stratford after 21:00</li>
	<li>Please use local buses</li>
</ul>

<p>Follow <a href="http://twitter.com/LondonDLR">&#64;LondonDLR</a> for news and service information.</p>

<hr />
<h2>London Trams</h2>

<p>A Sunday service is running today.</p>

<p>Follow <a href="http://twitter.com/tramslondon">&#64;TramsLondon</a> for news and service information.</p>

<hr />
<h2>Buses</h2>

<p>A Sunday service is running today:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Day routes start at normal Sunday times</li>
	<li>24-hour routes start from about 06:00</li>
	<li>See all today's planned bus changes on our <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/bus/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2018-12-26T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2018-12-26T23%3a59%3a59">Bus status updates map for Wednesday 26 December</a>.</li>
</ul>

<p>Follow <a href="https://twitter.com/TfLBusAlerts">&#64;TfLBusAlerts</a> for news and service information.</p>

<hr />
<h2>Driving</h2>

<ul>
	<li>There is a closure of the A127 for <a href="/travel-information/improvements-and-projects/a127-ardleigh-green-bridge">bridge work</a>&nbsp; between Gallows Corner and Squirrels Heath/Ardleigh Green Road westbound only until 05:00</li>
	<li>The Congestion Charge and T-Charge do not apply today</li>
	<li>See our <a href="http://tfl.gov.uk/traffic/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2018-12-26T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2018-12-26T23%3a59%3a59">traffic status updates map for 26 December</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Follow <a href="https://twitter.com/TfLTrafficNews">&#64;TfLTrafficNews</a> on Twitter.</p>

<hr />
<h2>Emirates Air Line</h2>

<p>Today the cable car is running 08:00-21:00.</p>

<p>See <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/cable-car/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2018-12-24T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2018-12-24T23%3a59%3a59">Status updates for Emirates&nbsp;Air Line on 26 December</a>&nbsp;or <a href="https://twitter.com/EmiratesAirLDN">follow &#64;EmiratesAirLine on Twitter</a>.</p>

<hr />
<h2>Taxis &amp; minicabs</h2>

<p>For taxis (black cabs) there is an extra charge of &pound;4 if you're travelling today. For private hire (including minicabs), there may be an extra charge -&nbsp;please check when you book.</p>

<hr />
<h2>River</h2>

<p>There are no Thames Clippers running today.</p>

<p>Follow<a href="https://twitter.com/tflriver">&nbsp;&#64;TfLRiver</a> for news and service information.</p>

<hr />
<h2>National Rail</h2>

<p>Check <a href="http://www.nationalrail.co.uk/service_disruptions/172038.aspx">National Rail's Christmas page</a> for information about service changes and planned works over Christmas and the New Year.</p>
      
           
      
      
        
          
